{"tid":1890834,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"真心推薦《串Grill 》黃店慢煮料理","createTime":"2020-02-21T11:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T12:32:11.000Z","uid":78533,"like":44,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f0585c8b0addb0be2fe80eae3dadbbcd7e49da74","tid":1890834,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T11:37:17.000Z","msg":"屌你老母！嬲撚到我！<br />\n廣華街間垃圾串Grill 個爐都唔撚熱 燒條毛 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未食個一間咗戇鳩既放題 乜撚野自助燒烤<br />\nd位迫撚到 隔硬黎 放個袋都難 <br />\n<br />\nd野食又唔係乜高級野 又學人唔撚調味 比幾隻燒烤粉你就算鳩數 真係識慳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n野食普通都唔緊要 比兩百幾預左唔好得去邊 <br />\n<br />\n但你老母臭閪 比兩個鐘你同我玩慢煮 個爐食撚左老人屎咁 <br />\n燒果兩粒丸10分鐘 又慢天唔撚熱 <br />\n真係直接含撚住舊野仲熱得快過佢 咪撚提燒肉類 <br />\n<br />\n再屌多次你老母臭閪 睇番openrice d臭閪打手真係全撚部都假 又係到用黃店作招來 屌 既然係黃店咁係我錯囉 只係我唔知呢間原來係食慢煮<br />\n<br />\n不過無下次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"895711d85b4b6771df16704c39e2136f1ad70217","tid":1890834,"uid":78533,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T11:41:57.000Z","msg":"屌 嬲撚到字都打錯晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總之大家睇路 唔係黃店就好 <br />\n<br />\n情願去食小貴既黃店cafe 起碼環境唔錯 飲杯野就算收成舊水都冇咗嬲"},{"pid":"f3a4cd61e4709da34aec4a1580def490bc2a2613","tid":1890834,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T11:45:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n太嬲 推到下左啖氣先停"},{"pid":"28a028845065d563228818666e71b9fc87c1893a","tid":1890834,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T11:57:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推 黃店"},{"pid":"08b41c158b7fbe5a14f336ee175472e959650b89","tid":1890834,"uid":153,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T12:02:26.000Z","msg":"想食好耐 多謝樓主<br />\n可以省返唔洗食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c53e6576380fc56eea99c9f34dd7e7dfd78c9134","tid":1890834,"uid":171451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T12:03:03.000Z","msg":"有無圖先"},{"pid":"98d5d7f2102db358b873f8d1c9bf7e43e9b08724","tid":1890834,"uid":79052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"08b41c158b7fbe5a14f336ee175472e959650b89","tid":1890834,"uid":153,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T12:02:26.000Z","msg":"想食好耐 多謝樓主<br />\n可以省返唔洗食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T12:08:42.000Z","msg":"+1<br />\n同班fd諗住去踩場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d96ebe9581ac6bdf94d2ac376d